summary:
**Meeting Overview**: The Dallas Area Partnership to End and Prevent Homelessness Local Government Corporation was scheduled to hold a meeting on Thursday, September 5, 2024, at 12:00 PM at Dallas City Hall. However, this meeting has been cancelled. The next meeting is set for October 3, 2024, at the same location and time.

**Key Agenda Items**: Since the meeting was cancelled, no specific agenda items were discussed or decisions made for this session. The upcoming meeting in October may address ongoing initiatives related to homelessness prevention and support.

**Important Details**: No significant proposals, budget items, policy changes, or projects were presented due to the cancellation of the meeting. The agenda for the next meeting remains to be determined.

**Action Items**: No decisions or approvals were sought in the cancelled meeting. Stakeholders are encouraged to prepare for the next meeting on October 3, 2024, where it is expected that relevant topics regarding homelessness will be addressed. Participants can join in person or via WebEx.
